author: kwall
msg: NO-JIRA: [Java Broker] Added new perf test script to test the varying consumer/producer batch size independently of the other. This simulates a use-case that has been problematic for previous Qpid versions.
Changed visualisation-jfc to allow the perf-test result summary page title to be specified from the command line.
Converted BatchSize script from JSON to Javascript.
